Usage: reportTimingLib [-help] [-outfile <string>] [[[-all  | -pin  | -threshold  | -sibling ] [<cellName>] [-byLib ]] | -lib <string>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<cellName>            # list of cell name (string, optional)
-all                  # prints all the pin properties, siblings of a cell, the
                      # libraries where they are defined, and the voltage.
                      # (bool, optional)
-byLib                # Organises the report by libraries. (bool, optional)
-lib <string>         # provide a single library name.The name should internal
                      # library name or delay_corner(internal_library_name)
                      # (string, optional)
-outfile <string>     # Output file name (string, optional)
-pin                  # reports the pin properties, such as the pin name,
                      # direction, capacitance, max load, max fanout, and
                      # fanout load. (bool, optional)
-sibling              # reports sibling cells, the libraries where they are
                      # defined, and the voltage. (bool, optional)
-threshold            # reports the input thresholds, output thresholds, and
                      # slew thresholds of a cell. (bool, optional)